---
title: Carb Smart Loaded Bunless Pork and Bacon Burgers with Arugula and Spinach
description: Any night can be burger night, but sometimes we leave the bun behind! Start with a nutritious salad base, then add juicy all-pork patties and pile on the tasty toppings real high.

